description:
PostSharp project "Caravela" compiler package.
      Referencing this package will cause the project to be built using the Caravela compiler contained in the package, as opposed to the version of the C# compiler installed with MSBuild.
      This package is not meant to be used directly and only serves as a dependency for Caravela.Framework and Caravela.Framework.Sdk.

      This package requires either MSBuild 16.3 and .NET Framework 4.7.2+ or .NET Core 3.1+.
